channel.title: Rage's Show To Go...
channel.description: A mixshow featuring new & unreleased music from signed/unsigned artists from around the world. It features Rap, Hip Hop, Reggae, Reggaeton & sometimes even dance music. Plus you never know when I will drop some classics and give you a trip down memory lane.
